Film star Rock Hudson and his death from Aids is recalled by friend and publicist Dale Olson. Also, César López, the young Colombian musician leading a musical crusade against violence. The civil servants in the West Bank and Gaza who aren't being paid as international funds have been cut off. Conflicted loyalties in Zimbabwe for a Black maid taking part in the farm invasion of her white employer's home. *NB - break in audio between 24:29-26:32* Show less